description:
Another great new diaper bag from Timi & Leslie. We love that nothing about this bag screams diapers, yet it is fully equipped to tote everything you need for your little one and keep it organized in the process. This is our favorite new convertible backpack option.

From Timi & Leslie:

The Hart Convertible Backpack takes the term convertible to a new level.  Not only is it a timi & leslie convertible diaper bag, but it’s also a backpack and a shoulder bag!  It’s super stylish and functional any which way you wear it!  It’s made from easy to clean faux leather (PVC free) and features our custom hardware in an antique brass finish. Hart comes with many functional and fashionable accessories and features:

-A cross body, adjustable detachable strap so you can wear it hands free whenever you need to;
-A detachable shoulder strap for when you want to carry it as a shoulder bag;
-Two adjustable detachable backpack straps for when you want to carry it as a backpack;
-Our specially designed changing pad with a front mesh pocket where you can store your diapers, wipes and creams when you need to make a quick diaper change trip;
-A zippered sac to put away soiled clothes; 
-A stylish clutch that you can use as your purse (who wants to carry a purse and a bebe bag?) with interior credit card slots and an inside zipper pocket;
-An insulated bottle tote to keep your baby's bottles warm or cool;
-Matching stroller straps so you can hang your bebe bag from your stroller;
-Water resistant, light colored lining so you can easily see everything in your bag;
-Five exterior pockets;
-Six interior organizational pockets;
-Inside key fob – never lose your keys!
-Bag Measures: 15”H x 14” W x 5” D and 8.5” handle drop 

Style # TL-227-01

Originally $180
